{
  "texts": [
    "While in Yang et al (2022), three DNN layers were integrated with the K-means algorithm based on the continuous values of student grades.",
    "Therefore, the combination of DNNs with either Ensemble Learning or ML techniques achieved prediction accuracy between 72% and 92.9%.",
    "Combining LSTM with other DL or ML techniques has been applied to student predictive models.",
    "In Dien et al (2020), LSTM was combined with CNN and integrated with Linear Regression (LR) algorithms to make predictions more accurate.",
    "Moreover, LSTM is combined with clustering, as in Waheed et al (2022) or with Decision Tree (DT) and Linear Regression (LR), as in Botelho et al (2019)."
  ]
}